scions.insc_term: Large and kind, great helpers of humanity
Animals actually born in December under Sagittarius

scions.insc_cntn: The best part of marrying you, Sagittarius, is the unpredictability. Even after being with you for years, you'll still keep them on their toes. You'll keep surprising them in new ways. They won't know exactly what to expect from you, so no two days will be exactly alike.
Sagittarians = should avoid stimulants and intoxicants, especially in excess amounts
Sagittarius = is a fiery, hot, and choleric sign, and so the individual intoxicated Sagittarius can easily get driven to extremes.
Sagittarians = are better-suited to a vegetarian (or at least a primarily-vegetarian) diet
